info.name: Aloo Paratha
info.description: Serves 1 | A flavorful and spiced potato stuffing, rolled inside a freshly made whole wheat dough, and cooked to perfection on a griddle. Served alongside a side of pickle and yogurt, this dish is perfect for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.

info.name: Aloo Pyaaz Paratha
info.description: Serves 1 | A mouthwatering filling of spiced potatoes and onions, rolled inside a freshly made whole wheat dough, and cooked to perfection on a griddle. Served alongside a side of pickle and yogurt, this dish is perfect for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.

info.name: Paneer Paratha
info.description: Serves 1 | A delicious and spiced paneer filling, rolled inside a freshly made whole wheat dough, and cooked to perfection on a griddle. Served alongside a side of pickle and yogurt, this dish is perfect for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.

info.name: Bhartiya Jalpan Special Paratha
info.description: Serves 1 | Indulge in the mouthwatering taste of our bhartiya jalpan special paratha, a unique and flavorful twist on the classic indian paratha. Experience the authentic taste of india with our bhartiya jalpan special paratha.

info.name: Bhujia Chilli Signature Paratha
info.description: Serves 1 | Made with bikaneri bhujia stuffed paratha mixed with special spices green chilli and onions to make a delicious innovative paratha. Served with our specail chilli pickle & raita

info.name: Fresh Malai Paneer
info.description: Serves 1 | Made with the finest ingredients and crafted with care. Savor the delectable and creamy taste of our fresh paneer, a quintessential indian dairy product that is sure to elevate your culinary experience. Freshly made using premium quality milk, expertly crafted into soft and velvety blocks, delivering a delicate and savory taste that is truly unparalleled.

info.name: Chola Bhatura
info.description: Serves 1 | Serve 2pc bhatura with spicy chole gravy cooked in a delectable veriety of masalas, served with a fluffy fried leavened bread serve

info.name: Club Kachori
info.description: Serves 1 | This traditional dish is made with a combination of crunchy kachori (fried pastry) and puri (deep-fried flatbread). The kachori is filled with a savory mixture of spices and is then topped with a spicy and flavorful mixture of chickpeas. Enjoy the unique flavors of india with every bite of this spicy and delicious club kachori 6pcs poori.

info.name: Poori Bhaji
info.description: Serves 1 | Enjoy the flavors of india with this delicious poori bhaji! this classic indian dish is made with a combination of puri (deep-fried flatbread) and bhaji (vegetable curry). The puri is topped with a flavorful and spicy vegetable curry for a truly unique and flavorful dish. Enjoy the spicy flavors of india with every bite of this delicious poori bhaji. Serve 3pcs poori

info.name: Rajasthani Dal Poori
info.description: Serves 1 | Experience the delicious flavors of rajasthan with rajasthani dal poori! this traditional dish is made with a combination of lentils, spices, and puri (deep-fried flatbread). The lentils are cooked until they are soft and flavorful, then topped with puri and seasoned with a variety of spices. Serve 3pcs poori

info.name: Matar Poori
info.description: Serves 1 | Crispy fried pooris (3pcs) mixed stuffed green peas served with spicy potato gravy

info.name: Paneer Chilla
info.description: Serves 1 | Enjoy a delicious and flavorful snack with this classic indian dish! paneer chilla is a savory pancake made with a mixture of paneer (a type of cheese), spices, and vegetables. It is then cooked on a hot griddle until golden brown and served hot. Enjoy the unique flavors of india with every bite of this spicy and delicious paneer chilla.

info.name: Kulcha Chola
info.description: Serves 1 | Baked indian flatbread brushed with butter served 2pc kulcha with chola

info.name: Chola Poori
info.description: Serves 1 | Chola poori is a traditional indian snack that is made with a combination of spiced chickpeas and puri (deep-fried flatbread). The perfect combination of crunchy and savory, it's sure to tantalize your taste buds! serve 3pcs poori

info.name: Chilla
info.description: Serves 1 | Tasty moongdal pancake made with spices and herbs .piping hot high in protien and a very healthy option .

info.name: Kachori (2 Pc)
info.description: Serves 1 | Lip smacking snack, straight from the land of flavourful rajasthan served with sweet and spicy chutney.

info.name: Punjabi Mini Aloo Samosa (4 Pc)
info.description: A perfect chai combo Punjabi samosa with north indian spices, served with mint chutney and tamarind chutney.

info.name: Punjabi Mini Samosa (5 Pc) With Ginger Masala Chai Flask (servers 4-5)
info.description: Punjabi samosa with north indian spices, served with mint chutney and tamarind chutney. Our unique blend of ginger, cinnamon, cloves, cardamom and black pepper creates a tantalizing and stimulating experience. Enjoy the warming and comforting taste of this deliciously spiced tea with milk or water. Perfect for any time of day, our ginger masala chai will leave you feeling refreshed and energised

info.name: Samosa (2 Pc)
info.description: Serves 1 | One of the most popular north indian snacks filled with special potato mixture served with sweet and green chutney for a hearty delicious snack.

info.name: Cheese Dhokla (2 Pc)
info.description: Serves 1 | Steamed healthy snack filled with cheese in the middle , tangy soft fluffy spongy and delicious snack for health freaks.

info.name: French Fries
info.description: Serves 1 | Crispy, golden-brown french fries are a beloved fast-food favorite. Their fluffy interior and crunchy exterior make them a delicious addition to any meal. With their savory flavor, they are a great snack or side dish.

info.name: Peri Peri Fries
info.description: Serves 1 | Introducing peri peri french fries ? the perfect combination of classic french fries with a zesty zing of peri peri prinkle. These crispy and golden fries are sure to tantalize your taste buds with a delightful kick of heat and flavor. With their irresistible crunch, these fries are sure to be a delicious side to any meal or snack.

info.name: Filter Coffee Flask ( Serves 2-3 )
info.description: Serves 1 | A strong coffee for the coffee lovers.

info.name: Ginger Masala Chai Flask (servers 2-3)
info.description: Serves 1 | Bhartiya jalpan's famous chai ! strong flavoured tea sourced from our home town assam with fresh ginger and our special masalas.

info.name: Filter Coffee Flask ( Serves 4-6 )
info.description: Serves 1 | It is made by slowly infusing freshly ground coffee beans into hot water, resulting in a strong, full-bodied cup of coffee. Rich and smooth, filter coffee is known for its deep flavour and intense aromas. With its beautiful aroma and robust taste, it is sure to provide the perfect pick-me-up for any time of the day.

info.name: Ginger Masala Chai Flask ( Serves 4-6 )
info.description: Serves 1 | A perfect combination of black tea and spices, our ginger masala chai is sure to tantalise your taste buds. Our unique blend of ginger, cinnamon, cloves, cardamom and black pepper creates a tantalizing and stimulating experience. Enjoy the warming and comforting taste of this deliciously spiced tea with milk or water. Perfect for any time of day, our ginger masala chai will leave you feeling refreshed and energised!

info.name: Rasgulla (2 Pc)
info.description: A bengali delicacy made of chenna and soaked in sugar syrup, these soft and spongy sweets are a must-try for those who love milk-based desserts. Veg Item. Rasmalai 2 Pcs. Costs: 90 rupees, Description: Similar to rasgulla, these milk-based sweets are soaked in flavoured milk and garnished with nuts for added flavour. Swipe right to add item to cart.

info.name: Rasmalai (2 Pc)
info.description: Similar to rasgulla, these milk-based sweets are soaked in flavoured milk and garnished with nuts for added flavour.

info.name: Badam Halwa (100 Gm)

info.name: Moong Dal Halwa (200gm)

info.name: Lassi
info.description: Serves 1 | Cool off with our refreshing lassi, a traditional yogurt-based drink that has been enjoyed for centuries in south asia. Our lassi is made with fresh, creamy yogurt blended with water and your choice of either sweet fruits or savory spices.

info.name: Buttermilk
info.description: Serves 1 | A refreshing and tangy drink that is perfect to accompany any meal. Made by blending fresh, creamy yogurt with water, our buttermilk is a healthy and nutritious beverage that aids in digestion and promotes gut health.

info.name: Masala Soda Shikanji
info.description: Serves 1 | Soda with lemon,chaat masala,black salt,cumin and mint

info.name: Pav Bhaji
info.description: Serves 1 | Piping hot gravy of hand pounded mixed vegetable, in a spicy tomato sauce. An absolute all - time favourite, served with soft buttery pav.

info.name: Pani Poori (6 Pc)
info.description: Serves 1 | Crispy small pooris (6pcs) filled with a potato mash filling dipped into a mixture of tangy and sweet water .

info.name: Papdi Chaat
info.description: Serves 1 | It is made from crunchy papdis (fried dough wafers) topped with a variety of tantalising ingredients. The papdis are layered with potatoes, chickpeas, yoghurt, chutneys, tamarind sauce, coriander and spices, and then garnished with boiled chickpeas, pomegranate seeds and crunchy sev. This delightful treat is a perfect balance of sweet, sour and spicy flavours. Papdi chaat is the perfect snack for whenever you're feeling a bit peckish!

info.name: Dahi Poori
info.description: Serves 1 | A delicious indian street food, made from deep fried puffed puris and filled with a tangy and spicy yogurt mixture. The combination of the crisp puris with the creamy, spiced yogurt is truly mouth-watering. The main ingredients include puris, yogurt, potatoes, onions, tomatoes, cilantro, chillies, tamarind chutney, chaat masala, and lime juice. These ingredients are combined to create a unique flavour that is sure to tantalise your taste buds

info.name: Raj Kachori
info.description: Serves 1 | A snack made from a deep-fried pastry filled with a variety of savoury ingredients. It is usually filled with potatoes, onions, chickpeas, and spices, and garnished with chutneys, yoghurt and sev. This crispy and flavourful dish is a popular street food in india. It is a great snack to enjoy with friends and family.

info.name: Dahi Bhalla
info.description: Serves 1 | It is made with a combination of fried lentil dumplings, yogurt, and various spices. The lentil dumplings are made with a mix of urad dal and chana dal, which has been soaked, ground, and then deep-fried. The yogurt is mixed with spices such as cardamom, cumin, and black pepper to create a creamy, tangy sauce. Finally, the dish is topped with various ingredients such as tamarind chutney, coriander, and sev to create a delicious and complex flavour.

info.name: Ragda Poori
info.description: Serves 1 | Ragda poori is a popular indian street snack, made with crisp fried puri, which is a type of unleavened flatbread, topped with a flavorful combination of spicy ragda and chutneys. The ragda is made from dried white peas cooked with a mixture of spices, while the chutneys typically include sweet tamarind, green coriander, and spicy mint. Topped with sev, this delicious snack is a vegan-friendly delight. Enjoy the crunchy texture of the puri

info.name: Masala Poori
info.description: Serves 1 | This delightful dish is then served with a spicy potato mix, cooked in a rich blend of herbs and spices, such as cumin, coriander, turmeric, chilli powder, garam masala, and ginger. The spiciness of the potatoes perfectly complements the crunchy, golden-brown poori, making it an irresistible snack or side dish.

info.name: Samosa Chaat Dahi
info.description: Serves 1 | A delicious and traditional indian dish. It is made with crispy samosas filled with spicy potatoes, onions and peas. It is topped with a tangy, sweet and sour chutney, a spicy tamarind sauce and a creamy yoghurt. This dish is garnished with fresh coriander, crunchy sev and pomegranate seeds. It is a perfect combination of sweet, sour and spicy flavours, making it a popular choice amongst indian food lovers.

info.name: Samosa Chaat Matar
info.description: Crushed samosas served over a bed of spicy green peas preparation and garnished with chutney topped with our special masalas.

info.name: Aloo Tikki Dahi
info.description: Serves 1 | This delicious indian dish, made from mashed potatoes, spices and herbs, and served with a creamy yoghurt sauce. The potatoes are mixed with spices such as cumin, coriander, turmeric and chilli, before being pan-fried until golden brown. The creamy yoghurt sauce is made from a combination of yoghurt, garlic and ginger, and is perfect for dipping the tikki in. A hearty and flavoursome dish, aloo tikki dahi is sure to satisfy.

info.name: Aloo Tikki Matar
info.description: Serves 1 | Shallow fried potato cutlets served over a bed of spicy green peas curry, garnished with tamarind and green chutneys topped with our special masalas

info.name: Kachori Chaat Dahi
info.description: Serves 1 | An indulgent and highly popular indian street food. It consists of a crisp and flaky kachori, a deep fried pastry, topped with an array of tantalising ingredients. The kachori is complemented by a generous helping of savoury potatoes and chickpeas, adding a delightful texture to the dish. It is then generously smothered in a tangy tamarind and yoghurt sauce, giving it a unique sweet and sour flavour. To finish, the kachori chaat dahi is sprinkled with crunchy sev, cumin powder

info.name: Palak Patta Chaat
info.description: Palak Patta Chaat has a mix of sweet, sour, spicy, and tangy flavors, and a crunchy and creamy texture. It is a great way to enjoy the health benefits of spinach in a tasty way

info.name: Lachha Tokri (potato Basket)
info.description: Serves 1 | Small baskets of fried potatoes are filled with boiled chana, potatoes, spicy and sweet chutneys and curd our special masalas.

info.name: Samosa Pav
info.description: Serves 1 | Hot samosa placed inside a sliced pav bun,favoured with spices and served with specially made powder & chutney

info.name: Tadke Wali Dal With Jeera Rice
info.description: Serves 1 | Soft melt-in-your mouth dal with special tadka tempered with spices and served beside a bed of basmati jeera rice, ( serve with raita / chips / onion and pickle)

info.name: Pindi Chole With Jeera Rice
info.description: Serves 1 | A popular punjabi dish made with chickpeas that are cooked in a spicy and tangy gravy. Served with jeera rice, this dish offers a perfect blend of flavors and textures that are sure to leave you wanting more.

info.name: Rajma Masala With Jeera Rice
info.description: Serves 1 | A north indian delicacy made with kidney beans cooked in a spicy tomato-based gravy. Served with jeera rice, this dish is a perfect combination of protein and carbohydrates, making it a wholesome and satisfying meal.

info.name: Paneer Gravy With Jeera Rice
info.description: Serves 1 | This delectable dish features succulent chunks of paneer cooked in a rich and aromatic gravy, served with fluffy jeera rice. The flavors of the spices and herbs used in the gravy perfectly complement the creaminess of the paneer, making it a treat for the taste buds.

info.name: Makki Ki Roti / Sarson Ka Saag (seasonal)
info.description: Serves 1 | Makki roti (2pcs) topped with white butter and served with sarson ka saag & gur (jaggery).

info.name: Papad Bhurji
info.description: Serves 1 | It's very flavorful, mouth-watering snack, this traditional indian dish is made with a delicious blend of potatoes, onions, and spices, cooked in hot oil to give it a wonderfully spicy kick. Enjoy it as a side dish or snack, and you won't be disappointed!

info.name: Boondi Raita
info.description: Boondi raita is a traditional indian dish that packs a flavorful punch! made with yogurt, spices, and boondi, this dish is a perfect accompaniment to any meal. The yogurt is cooling, the spices are zesty, and the boondi add a delightful crunch. This flavorful raita is sure to tantalize your taste buds and add a spicy kick to your meal.

info.name: Mixed Raita
info.description: Loaded with aromatic spices, crunchy veggies and succulent fruits, it's a delight for your tongue. If you're looking to add some indian flair to your meal, look no further than mixed raita!. A true taste of india! this cool, creamy and tangy yogurt-based condiment is the perfect accompaniment to any meal.

info.name: Dal Fry
info.description: Enjoy the wholesome taste of our dal fry, a classic vegetarian dish from north india that is both nutritious and delicious. Made with yellow lentils, simmered with a blend of aromatic spices and tempered with cumin seeds, garlic, and onions, creating a flavorful and hearty dish. Served alongside basmati rice, naan bread, and a side of raita, this meal is both filling and satisfying.

info.name: Dal Tadka
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic indian dish that is both nutritious and flavorful. Made with yellow lentils, simmered with a blend of aromatic spices and tempered with ghee, cumin seeds, garlic, and onions, creating a rich and satisfying dish. Served alongside basmati rice, naan bread, and a side of raita, this meal is perfect for any time of the day.

info.name: Dal Makhani
info.description: Savor the rich and creamy taste of our dal makhani, a classic north indian dish made with black lentils, kidney beans, and a blend of aromatic spices. Our dal makhani is slow-cooked to perfection in a creamy tomato-based sauce, creating a melt-in-your-mouth texture that is sure to leave you satisfied. This dish is served alongside rice, bread, and a side of raita, making it a complete and wholesome meal.

info.name: Dhaba Dal
info.description: Serves 1 | A healthy mix of all lentil preparation made with desi ghee and spices to give you a pure dhaba feel.

info.name: Ghee Phulka (2 Pc)
info.description: Serves 1 | A traditional indian flatbread made of whole wheat flour.

info.name: Plain Phulka (2 Pc)
info.description: Serves 1 | A traditional indian flatbread made of whole wheat flour.

info.name: Jeera Rice
info.description: Serves 1 | A simple preparation of perfectly cooked basmati rice brought alive by the freshness of cumin.

info.name: Panner Roll
info.description: The stuffing is a lip-smacking paneer tikka made on skillet, a vibrant green chutney and a crunchy mixed veggie salad.

info.name: Veg Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | A delectable and wholesome snack that is perfect for satisfying those hunger pangs. Made with a variety of fresh vegetables like carrots, capsicum, onion, cabbage, and spiced with a range of aromatic herbs and spices, this snack is a perfect blend of flavors and textures.

info.name: Tawa Aloo Cheese Toast
info.description: Melt in the mouth experience with this chesse aloo sandwich

info.name: Tawa Aloo Toast
info.description: Our spicy  chatpata aloo masala sandwich make with pure butter inTawa.

info.name: Tawa Chilli Cheese Toast
info.description: Covered in cheese chilli and desi spices grilled inTawa for a desi feel.

info.name: Tawa Pizza Toast
info.description: When west meets east a perfect fusion of imported sauses and desi masalas for this special tawa pizza sandwich
